11#import <Foundation/Foundation.h>
12
13#import "RTCCodecSpecificInfo.h"
14#import "RTCEncodedImage.h"
15#import "RTCMacros.h"
16#import "RTCVideoEncoderSettings.h"
17#import "RTCVideoFrame.h"
18
19NS_ASSUME_NONNULL_BEGIN
20
21/** Callback block for decoder. */
22typedef void (^RTCVideoDecoderCallback)(RTCVideoFrame *frame);
23
24/** Protocol for decoder implementations. */
25RTC_OBJC_EXPORT
26@protocol RTCVideoDecoder <NSObject>
27
28- (void)setCallback:(RTCVideoDecoderCallback)callback;
29- (NSInteger)startDecodeWithNumberOfCores:(int)numberOfCores;
30- (NSInteger)releaseDecoder;
31- (NSInteger)decode:(RTCEncodedImage *)encodedImage
32 missingFrames:(BOOL)missingFrames
33 codecSpecificInfo:(nullable id<RTCCodecSpecificInfo>)info
34 renderTimeMs:(int64_t)renderTimeMs;
35- (NSString *)implementationName;
36
37@end
38
39NS_ASSUME_NONNULL_END
